author: @kamran_desu
text: KNN training time is correctly NA here, it is a lazy classifier - O(1). It only predicts at run time by calculating distance to nearest neighbours. It's too computationally intensive O(n.d) if applied in a naive way, so need to use kd-tree / ball tree / apply dimensionality reduction.
